' @id(SEQ-VIEW-DEPLOY)  <<added>> this cycle (0010) — new file
' @ref(USE-VIEW-DEPLOY)
' @ref(DOM-RENDER-ENGINE)
' Cycle 0010 diff (current side): whole diagram added, nothing removed.
title mdd view — surface .mdd/deploy via a third source · cycle 0010 diff (current)

actor "Developer" as Dev <<added>>
participant "mdd-cli\nCommands::View" as Cli <<added>>
participant "MddViewer::new()" as Viewer <<added>>
participant "Project::deploy_files()" as Core <<added>>
participant "render_sources(\nRenderTree::Deploy)" as RT <<added>>
database ".mdd/deploy/**/*.puml" as Deploy <<added>>
database ".mdd/rendered/deploy/**/*.svg" as Rendered <<added>>

Dev -> Cli : mdd view
Cli -> Viewer : run(project) -> MddViewer::new

group Two parity-gated sources (unchanged)
  Viewer -> Viewer : model_registry()  (.mdd/models + .mdd/constraints)
  Viewer -> Viewer : cycle_registry()  (.mdd/cycles)
end

group Third source — deploy_files() (NOT gated)  [ADDED 0010]
  Viewer -> Core : project.deploy_files()
  Core -> RT : render_sources(RenderTree::Deploy)
  RT -> Deploy : walk_suffix(".mdd/deploy", ".puml")
  Deploy --> RT : [diagram.puml ...]
  RT --> Core : sources
  Core -> Core : per file: extract_ids/refs,\nrendered_pages_for(rel)\n-> ModelFile{ kind=Other, side=Shared }
  note right of Core
    NOT inserted into ModelRegistry, so
    /mdd-validate and /mdd-review never
    see .mdd/deploy/.
  end note
  Core --> Viewer : Vec<ModelFile> -> self.deploy_files
end

Viewer -> Viewer : update(): TreeNode::build(deploy)\n"DEPLOY · /mdd-deploy · utility, not parity-gated"\n(Directory AND By-cycle)
Dev -> Viewer : click deploy leaf
Viewer -> Viewer : lookup_file(path) -> load_file(file)
Viewer -> Rendered : read .mdd/rendered/deploy/<rel>.svg
Rendered --> Viewer : SVG bytes -> DiagramPage
Viewer --> Dev : deployment diagram painted on canvas

note over Deploy, Rendered
  No .svg mirror -> same "No rendered output" placeholder
  as any unrendered model. `mdd render` covers
  RenderTree::Deploy; the viewer never rasterizes.
end note
@enduml
